  "title": "LLM 是否改善了患者的治疗效果？",
  "url": "https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/have-llms-improved-patient-outcomes",
  "date": "2026-05-03 20:00:14",
  "author": "Gary Marcus",
  "siteName": "Marcus on AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\">\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260503204248_fdcba01c-1594-4472-a23d-221981a1445c_1800x2003.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260503204248_fdcba01c-1594-4472-a23d-221981a1445c_1800x2003.jpeg 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260503204249_fdcba01c-1594-4472-a23d-221981a1445c_1800x2003.jpeg 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260503204249_fdcba01c-1594-4472-a23d-221981a1445c_1800x2003.jpeg 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260503204249_fdcba01c-1594-4472-a23d-221981a1445c_1800x2003.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260503204249_fdcba01c-1594-4472-a23d-221981a1445c_1800x2003.jpeg\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/fdcba01c-1594-4472-a23d-221981a1445c_1800x2003.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1620,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:2739957,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/196345367?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffdcba01c-1594-4472-a23d-221981a1445c_1800x2003.jpeg&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260503204248_fdcba01c-1594-4472-a23d-221981a1445c_1800x2003.jpeg 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260503204249_fdcba01c-1594-4472-a23d-221981a1445c_1800x2003.jpeg 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260503204249_fdcba01c-1594-4472-a23d-221981a1445c_1800x2003.jpeg 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260503204249_fdcba01c-1594-4472-a23d-221981a1445c_1800x2003.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n     <figcaption class=\"image-caption\">Artwork by Dave Coverly at Speedbump.com. Reprinted by perrmission.</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>Cardiologist/author </span><span style=\"min-width:0;\" data-state=\"closed\"><a href=\"https://open.substack.com/users/1923753-eric-topol?utm_source=mentions\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Eric Topol&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:1923753,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;user&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:null,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6aac3e1d-17aa-405e-953b-393d7253107b_511x511.png&quot;,&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;d8418e40-fe7b-4168-9108-e8af6377af54&quot;}\" data-component-name=\"MentionUser\" class=\"mention-pnpTE1\">Eric Topol</a></span><span> tends to be more bullish than I am about AI in medicine, but in his latest post he concludes that at least thus far there is “very little evidence for LLMs benefiting patients or doctors for health outcomes” (aside from helping with administrative work and the like). </span></p>\n   <p><span>As Topol notes, his review was partly inspired by this</span><a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-026-04389-4\"> recent editorial in Nature Medicine</a><span>, which points in the same direction:</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260503204249_ea3bfcfa-1514-4ec8-a994-c945ecbbec3a_1613x1343.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260503204248_ea3bfcfa-1514-4ec8-a994-c945ecbbec3a_1613x1343.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260503204248_ea3bfcfa-1514-4ec8-a994-c945ecbbec3a_1613x1343.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260503204249_ea3bfcfa-1514-4ec8-a994-c945ecbbec3a_1613x1343.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260503204249_ea3bfcfa-1514-4ec8-a994-c945ecbbec3a_1613x1343.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260503204249_ea3bfcfa-1514-4ec8-a994-c945ecbbec3a_1613x1343.png\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ea3bfcfa-1514-4ec8-a994-c945ecbbec3a_1613x1343.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1212,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:199430,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/196345367?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fea3bfcfa-1514-4ec8-a994-c945ecbbec3a_1613x1343.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260503204248_ea3bfcfa-1514-4ec8-a994-c945ecbbec3a_1613x1343.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260503204248_ea3bfcfa-1514-4ec8-a994-c945ecbbec3a_1613x1343.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260503204248_ea3bfcfa-1514-4ec8-a994-c945ecbbec3a_1613x1343.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260503204249_ea3bfcfa-1514-4ec8-a994-c945ecbbec3a_1613x1343.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>You can read Topol’s detailed review </span><a href=\"https://open.substack.com/pub/erictopol/p/the-paradox-of-medical-ai-implementation?r=8tdk6&amp;utm_medium=ios\">here</a><span>. </span></p>\n   <p><span>All of this fits with my recent </span><a href=\"https://open.substack.com/pub/garymarcus/p/please-dont-trust-your-chatbot-for?r=8tdk6&amp;utm_campaign=post-expanded-share&amp;utm_medium=web\">Please don’t trust your chatbot for medical advice</a><span>, which focused more on unsupervised use of LLMs by patients, rather than overall clinical outcomes, but in many ways converges to a similar place.</span></p>\n   <p>AI will surely someday be a major boon for medicine, but current tools such as domain-general chatbots may not be up to the job.</p>\n   <div data-component-name=\"SubscribeWidget\" class=\"subscribe-widget\">\n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-justifyContent-center pc-reset\">\n     <div class=\"container-IpPqBD\">\n      <form action=\"/api/v1/free?nojs=true\" method=\"post\" novalidate class=\"form form-M5sC90\">\n       <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_url\" value><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_referrer\" value><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_url\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_referrer\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_url\" value><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_referrer\" value><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referral_code\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"source\" value=\"subscribe-widget\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referring_pub_id\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"additional_referring_pub_ids\">\n       <div class=\"sideBySideWrap-vGXrwP\">\n        <div class=\"emailInputWrapper-QlA86j\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-minWidth-0 pc-position-relative pc-reset flex-auto-j3S2WA\">\n          <input name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Type your email...\" type=\"email\" class=\"pencraft emailInput-OkIMeB input-y4v6N4 inputText-pV_yWb\">\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"submit\" disabled class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft rightButton primary subscribe-btn button-VFSdkv buttonBase-GK1x3M\"><span class=\"button-text \">Subscribe</span></button>\n       </div>\n      </form>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文认为，尽管炒作不断，但目前几乎没有证据表明 LLM 改善了患者的健康结果，其益处主要局限于行政任务。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文认为，尽管炒作不断，但目前几乎没有证据表明 LLM 改善了患者的健康结果，其益处主要局限于行政任务。",
  "summary": "这篇文章由 Gary Marcus 撰写，批判性地审视了大型语言模型（LLM）目前在医学领域对患者结果的影响。文章引用了心脏病学家 Eric Topol 最近的评论，该评论得出结论称，除了行政工作之外，“几乎没有证据表明 LLM 对患者或医生的健康结果有益”。Marcus 将此与《自然医学》的一篇社论以及他自己先前关于警告不要无监督使用医疗聊天机器人的工作联系起来。核心论点是，虽然 AI 未来很可能会成为医学的一大福音，但当前的通用领域聊天机器人还不足以胜任改善临床结果的工作。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "当前的 LLM 几乎没有显示出改善患者健康结果的证据。",
      "explanation": "文章引用了 Eric Topol 的评论和《自然医学》的社论，两者都得出结论认为益处主要局限于行政任务，而非临床结果。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通用领域聊天机器人不适合用于无监督的医疗建议。",
      "explanation": "Marcus 重申了他之前的立场，即患者不应信任聊天机器人提供的医疗建议，因为当前的工具对于此类关键应用来说还不够可靠。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 在医学领域的未来充满希望，但当前的工具尚不充分。",
      "explanation": "文章承认了 AI 在医疗保健领域的长期潜力，但强调当前的通用领域 LLM 尚无法提供有意义的临床改进。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "几乎没有证据表明 LLM 对患者或医生的健康结果有益",
    "AI 未来某天必将成为医学的一大福音，但当前诸如通用领域聊天机器人之类的工具可能还不足以胜任这项工作。"
  ],
